<br>
Mel sat down on a nearby chair. Wipping her eyes with the edge of her outfit. She managed a weak smile and nodded her head in reply yes to the food. She was starving from the ride and the rain didn't help her mood any.<br>
<br>
Finaly she managed to speak, &quot;Is there any... word on... my sister? Do you Know... where she is?...How are... we going to save her?&quot; <p>~*~ Melanippe &quot;black Horse&quot; ~*~ <br>
