<br>
&quot;Call back the others, if any hunger, let them feed at will.&quot;<br>
<br>
With that, every hidden wolf in the area gave a loud mystical howl and darted into the village tearing at the men as they could. Alysia herself liked the taste of the high generals, so since Solari said not to harm the one who took Hippolyte, Alysia took off after his second in command.<br>
She grinned as he aimed a spear at her, his eyes widened when she lept into the air and caught it in her teeth breaking it in half. He turned around to run but before he could make it anywhere, the white wolf Queen was on his back tearing and ripping her teeth into muscles and nerves.<br>
<br>
When he was dead, she looked around as her wolves and athelfi bathed the ground in blood. Odessa was among them, and the pride in her heart grew so much.<br>
She gave a loud howl in honor of the amazons and then turned away making her marks back towards where Solari stood.<br>
<br>
Alysia gave a nod to Solari and stood about 15 feet away from her and the Roman. Alysia wanted to watch this, and make sure that if any other Romans came near Hippolyte's hut, Alysia would be their killer. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#993300>- </font><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite>Amazons Unite</a><font color=#993300> - </font><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66>Anatolia / Ancient Turkey </a> <font color=#993300> - </font><a href="http://pub163.ezboard.com/bmythicalodysseyforum">Home</a><font color=#993300> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.3m<br>Copyright ©1999-2003 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  

